Title: Last Hurrah: Dragon Isles
Description:
You've become quite popular with our allies, $n!

To the south the Iskaara Tuskarr need your help with their community feast.

To the west the Maruuks have requested your aid with their hunts.

To the north the Obsidian Outcasts request your help reclaiming Dragonbane Keep.

Sounds like you have a full day ahead of you! Best of luck.
ObjectivesText: Assist the Tuskarr with their community feast, the Maruuk with their Hunt, and help reclaim Dragonbane Keep.
